# 📸 Image Placeholder Directory

This here folder is fer storin' screenshots and graphics fer the README!

Since we're usin' ASCII art diagrams instead of real screenshots (they work everywhere, y'all!),
this folder might stay empty. But if ya wanna add real screenshots later, here's what ya need:

## If Ya Wanna Add Real Screenshots Later:

1. **Telegram Bot Screenshots:**
   - `botfather_search.png` - Searchin' fer @BotFather
   - `botfather_newbot.png` - Creatin' a new bot
   - `bot_token.png` - The token ya git (CENSOR IT!)
   - `chat_id.png` - Gittin' yer Chat ID from @userinfobot
   - `bot_menu.png` - The bot's menu when ya send /start

2. **Railway Screenshots:**
   - `railway_login.png` - The login page
   - `railway_new_project.png` - Startin' a new project
   - `railway_select_repo.png` - Pickin' yer repository
   - `railway_variables.png` - Where ya put them variables
   - `railway_deploy_success.png` - Green deploy = happy times!

## Tips fer Screenshots:

- 🔴 ALWAYS censor sensitive info (tokens, IDs, keys)!
- 📏 Keep images around 800px wide fer best display
- 🖼️ Use PNG format fer better quality
- ✏️ Add arrows/circles to highlight important areas
- 🌙 Light theme screenshots work best fer readability

## Why We Use ASCII Art Instead:

1. ✅ Works in EVERY markdown viewer
2. ✅ No broken image links
3. ✅ Always up-to-date (no outdated screenshots)
4. ✅ Loads instantly - no waitin'!
5. ✅ Easy to edit directly in the README
6. ✅ Fun hillbilly vibe!
